If your payment has failed, here are some solutions you can try:
- Check your card details are correct and try again;
- Check if 3DS authentication is working correctly or showing up in your banking app;
- Make sure there’s enough money in the account you’re paying from;
- Try again with a different card;
- If you have a Revolut account, try purchasing crypto from the 'Crypto' section using your account balance.
If none of these steps work, please reach out to us and we’ll look into this for you.
